            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Neuron Labs School has been an incredible experience for my son, who is currently in 1st grade. He thoroughly enjoys attending school every day, thanks to the nurturing and engaging environment. The innovative curriculum fosters a love for learning and encourages creativity and critical thinking. Today, he was especially excited about Fathers Day, which was wonderfully organized and promoted teamwork and physical fitness. The dedication of the teachers and staff to provide a holistic education is truly commendable. I am thrilled with the positive impact Neuron Labs is having on his overall development.",
          "publisher": {
