            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Neuronlabs school provides a nurturing environment where young learners thrive. The dedicated teachers ensure a balance of play-based learning and foundational academics, fostering a love for learning early on. The classrooms are vibrant and engaging, equipped with age-appropriate resources that encourage exploration and curiosity. Safety and care are prioritized, creating a supportive atmosphere for each child to develop socially and academically. Parental involvement is welcomed, enhancing the partnership between home and school.",
